parameters: We've defeated it! The hunt is complete!

It's kinda complicated knowing that this means our
relationship is over, though.
Don't be so sentimental. It was you who said it, wasn't it?
You should have earned enough money with my help by now.
You should be grateful, not complaining.
I get it, I get it—just feeling a bit sad, that's all.
But hey, the job's done now.

The promise to obey me is still valid for today,
right?\I[12]
Well... yes, I suppose it's fine for today.
It's to sever our ties without any lingering feelings.
Say whatever you want, I'll indulge you just for today.
Heh heh\I[12] You say the nicest things\I[12]

(Even through the clothes, it's clear... that huge thing
I've seen so many times...\I[12])

(Having said 'anything goes'... I can't complain about
whatever play he demands...\I[12])

(Will he attack me right here...? It's possible, given how
excited he looks...\I[12])

(He'll surely take me home... and do me over and over until
just before the day ends...\I[12])

(I'm definitely not expecting anything... but my body is
already preparing to accept him...\I[12])

Suddenly, I feel guilty about everything we've done up to
now.
Like I'm regaining my conscience at the very last moment.
Anyway, I won't do anything erotic anymore.

Let's end both this job and our relationship cleanly with
this.
Are you sure...? Is that really okay...?
Don't tell me you want me to hold you, Captain?
Ridiculous...! There's no way I would say such a thing...!
I'm just taken aback by how abruptly it ended, that's all.

So our relationship is over! Of course, I have no
objections!

That's great, isn't it? From now on, live happily with your
husband.
I don't need you to tell me that.
